# KiCad Schematic for STM32 Flight Controller
EESchema Schematic File Version 2.0
# Components List:
# 1. STM32F407VGT6
# 2. MPU9250
# 3. MS5611
# 4. MAX7456
# 5. W25Q128
# 6. GPS
# 7. USB connector
# 8. Power regulators (LDOs, Buck converters, etc.)
# 9. PWM output connectors
# 10. SWD connector

#
# Connections:
#

# STM32F407VGT6 Connections
U1 STM32F407VGT6
  - VDD from Power Regulator (3.3V)
  - GND to Ground
  - SWDIO and SWCLK to SWD Connector
  - PWM Outputs to PWM connectors
  - USB Data lines to USB Connector
  - I2C/SPI lines to MPU9250, MS5611, MAX7456, and W25Q128
  - GPIOs for GPS module interface

# MPU9250 Connections
U2 MPU9250
  - VCC to 3.3V Power
  - GND to Ground
  - I2C/SPI lines to STM32F407

# MS5611 Connections
U3 MS5611
  - VDD to 3.3V Power
  - GND to Ground
  - I2C/SPI lines to STM32F407

# MAX7456 Connections
U4 MAX7456
  - VCC to 5V Power
  - GND to Ground
  - SPI lines to STM32F407

# W25Q128 Connections
U5 W25Q128
  - VCC to 3.3V Power
  - GND to Ground
  - SPI lines to STM32F407

# GPS Connections
U6 GPS Module
  - VCC to 3.3V Power
  - GND to Ground
  - UART lines to STM32F407

# Power Regulators
U7 Power Regulator
  - Input Voltage from Battery
  - Output to STM32F407 and peripherals

# Define other peripherals and interconnects similarly...

#
# End of Schematic